<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>SiteSprout - Launch Your Restaurant Website</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <style> /* small per-page tweaks kept minimal */
    .hero { padding: 6rem 0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header class="site-header">
      <div class="container header-inner">
      <div class="logo">SiteSprout</div>
      <nav>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/auth/google">Sign in with Google</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="hero dark-hero">
      <div class="container hero-inner">
        <h1 class="hero-title">Launch a Professional Restaurant Website — Instantly.</h1>
        <p class="hero-sub">SiteSprout generates a polished, mobile‑responsive website from your menu, brand colors, and images — no coding required.</p>
        <div class="hero-ctas">
          <a class="btn cta large" href="/admin">Build Your Custom Site</a>
          <a class="btn ghost" href="#how">How It Works</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="how" class="how-it-works">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">How It Works</h2>
        <p class="lead" style="text-align:center;max-width:880px;margin:0 auto 1.5rem;color:var(--color-muted);">Three simple steps take you from setup to a live website — all managed inside the Admin Builder.</p>
        <div class="steps">
          <div class="step card-glass">
            <div class="step-icon">1</div>
            <h3>Enter Details</h3>
            <p class="muted">Add your menu, images and descriptions in an intuitive form.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="step card-glass">
            <div class="step-icon">2</div>
            <h3>Pick a Theme</h3>
            <p class="muted">Choose colors and layout; see a live preview as you edit.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="step card-glass">
            <div class="step-icon">3</div>
            <h3>Launch Live</h3>
            <p class="muted">SiteSprout publishes a unique URL and serves your site dynamically.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-site">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="about-grid">
          <div>
            <h2 class="section-title">Why SiteSprout</h2>
            <p class="lead">A purpose-built CMS that automates professional site creation for restaurants — fast, visual, and reliable.</p>
            <a class="btn ghost" href="/admin">Open Admin Builder</a>
          </div>

          <div class="tech-highlights card-glass">
            <h3 class="subheading">Technical Highlights</h3>
            <ul class="muted">
              <li><strong>Dynamic Rendering:</strong> EJS templates inject MongoDB content into a single master design.</li>
              <li><strong>Asset Management:</strong> Multer handles uploads for logos and photos.</li>
              <li><strong>Modern UI:</strong> Glassmorphism and responsive layouts for a premium look.</li>
              <li><strong>MVC Architecture:</strong> Structured with Mongoose, EJS and Express.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="site-footer">
    <div class="container">© SiteSprout</div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
